➜中国人都很少知道的黄山小村庄，却是老外最爱，这个古村不简单
http://www.sohu.com/a/417909032_102365	19662
<p><strong>Day02</strong></p>
<p>食宿：猪栏酒吧乡村客栈碧山店</p>
<p>游荡：老油厂店、碧山村</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200912/c2f926889d064840a7c089a316a87af8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200912/14b8bed1e6284d7cb3591b5d25c31139.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200912/a6f0252fe9064df18c5908b8470391eb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
